snippet.title: Awesomenauts Assemble! PS4 Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
http://www.awesomenauts.com
http://www.facebook.com/Awesomenauts
http://twitter.com/RonimoGames

The Awesomenauts are back for more with Awesomenauts Assemble! Returning to the console battlegrounds once more, the Awesomenauts are bigger and better than ever!

Awesomenauts Assemble! is a MOBA fitted into the form of an accessible 3-on-3 action platformer. Head out to the online battlefields together with your friends as an online party or in local splitscreen, and never worry about having to wait for an online match because of drop-in matchmaking!
